snippet.title: Tempopo - Official Release Date Trailer | ID@Xbox
snippet.description:
Check out gameplay and explore the vibrant world of Tempopo in this new cute new trailer for the upcoming music puzzle game. Tempopo is a psychedelic soundscape in the sky. Puzzle through the seasons by conducting chaotic Tempopo to rescue musical flowers. Design and populate your melodic garden, then let the music play! 
Tempopo will be available on Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, and Xbox Game Pass on April 17, 2025. It is also coming to PC and Nintendo Switch.

#IGN #Gaming
